plot: Supergirl finds an opportunity to escape from the Phantom Zone but it comes with some dangerous strings attached; Lena joins the Super Friends on a mission but finds she disagrees with their plan of action.

The tower team try to deal with the spread of Prime "infecting" the citizens of National City, turning them into Progeny. To stop Prime, Alex will have to make the ultimate sacrifice - and Lean proves uncooperative. In the Phantom Zone, Supergirl has an ally turn against her as she and Zor-El find a way to escape via the Anchor.—Gislef
